isment which requires administrative access to run and is morethan likely one of the causes for autosave points to crash your machine.If you would like your machine to crash more times in the one playthrough of a game than over the last 3 years, by all means buy this game.  If you want ot keep your sanity and send a message to Ubisoft that PC gamers will not put up with a half♥♥♥♥♥♥♥job then do not buy this game."
