d to.-Uplay. Need I say more?TLDR;A pretty good looking shooting romp around a paradise island that I think most people would be able to play. Story is OK if not a little weird. A few technical glitches hold this game back from being highly recommend, but if you can overlook that it’s still a decent game. I’ve played much worse so I say give it a shot."
