iling because they are pirates in human trafficing and drug trade. But, it is the fact that it was made by design to have the primary villians be people of color and you can only play as a wealthy, white dude.I would be okay with racist elements, meaning I would still think they are racist, if the game was still enjoyable and redeamable in other aspects but the other aspects, I thought, were ""just okay"" making the game not recomendable.TL:DR It's okay. But, not good enough."
