,Recommended,220240,8669634,"Posted: 11 January, 2014",all,Travis,"Overall I enjoyed playing Far Cry 3. The story was amazing and the developers did a good job on portraying the aspect of building relationships with the people you meet along the way. When I say this game has a good story I mean the gameplay flows nicely and the concept of the story is really intresting. But to be completly honest with you this game is a really sad game if you think about it. First off everyone on the island except for the civilians living there has a problem. What was once a peaceful island turned into an absolute power struggle  between three waring factions. Not only that but if you think of it many of these factions were into bad habits such as killing innocent people for money and doing drugs and the worst part is they learned to enjoy it. What's even sadder about this game is ""you"" as a character also fell responsible for killing people and thourghout the game your chracter starts getting used to it like it's an everday thing. Although, you were trying to save your friends at the end of the game your character comes to realize that he has turned into something that he does not want to be and what he has done on the island will always be in his memory. This is why I find the game sad. One thing I didn't like about the game was the Multiplayer I had many issues with connecting to servers and even if I did get into a server tons of host migration were soon to follow which disrupted the gameplay to a point were the game was unplayable and in my opinion the Far Cry series is more of a single player game rather than a multiplayer game. Eventhough, this was the first Far Cry game I played I can't wait for the next Far Cry to come out and I can't wait to see what it has to offer.Below I have posted an overall layout about the pros and cons of this game.PROS:-Great Story Mode.-Amazing Graphics.-Open World.-Vehicles.-Great gameplay experience no lag in singleplayer.-The game is still fun and offers you challaning things to do after you have completed the story.CONS:-Terrible Multiplayer."
