d to sell to get even more money. Oh yeah, you can also pickup relics, letters, memory cards... yay. The letters are just another drop to the shallow story.hunting: kill animal X to get Y amount of pelts to craft item Z so you can carry more of something. done.QTE!!!and there is a lot more to talk about...To sum it up, I did sometimes enjoy the game, but found it average at best, it has no replay value whatsoever especially being that easy and repetetive... I honestly can not believe the hype about the game."
