ame look very nice. However in the middle of a thick jungle at night time without lamps and such it isn't actually dark.The game allows Alt tabbing, but don't expect to be able to play it once you've tabbed back in. It becomes unplayable.Aside from some good visuals and good charcters (the main bad guy is actually really decent and intresting) the game is weak in so many areas. I'm glad i picked it up for £3.75 last Christmas. I would have been devastated to pay full price for this effort.Avoid it and play a better shooter unless you're after a pretty looking no brainer FPS to hold your hand as you play."
